snippet.title: Mutant Football League - PC Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Mutant Football League is NOW AVAILABLE on PC/Steam; and is scheduled to release on PlayStation 4 / Xbox One in early 2018.

Steam Store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/529520/Mutant_Football_League/

This video highlights the brutality, finality, and humor that sets The MFL apart from all the other football games out there.

This new MFL game is being developed on the Unity Engine by Digital Dreams Entertainment, led by the creator/designer of the original Mutant League sports series that was a #1 hit on the Sega Genesis.
